{"tid":2190554,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"為拯救送中12人，我哋急需國際線向中共施壓","createTime":"2020-09-05T18:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T04:36:59.000Z","uid":173326,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1b65c6bc49e3e6859c5bee25484eeca602d19a74","tid":2190554,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:28:19.000Z","msg":"香港本土因為黨安法，政治人物同唔敢公開要求國際關注。<br />\n中共最注重外貿，如果有國際聲音表示關注送中12人嘅狀況，佢哋最少唔會有即時生命危險。<br />\n請各位國際線嘅知名人士可以優先處理呢件事，例如受訪時候要優先提及同講解。"},{"pid":"1ebbe078bb72c8406d54ab922a3e41733faf778a","tid":2190554,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0476cdc2283408786f664fb7e4398d2d755cad61","tid":2190554,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:33:17.000Z","msg":"海外嘅羅冠聰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbe4f70a8c6183bec40a3b4db71daa24fb9e53b","tid":2190554,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:34:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f16361090860dbe49b1260f13a094e2463bd42b","tid":2190554,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b467f2c4747a5456757b8e8f7a1584c537e9461","tid":2190554,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:38:19.000Z","msg":"其實唔抱太大期望，人哋鬼佬照拉照鎖"},{"pid":"1f0c970783c344f879a6ac9f0f2140196a4a9ca6","tid":2190554,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T18:53:27.000Z","msg":"支解香港重光先有機會出返黎架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smil